quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  22,73,logo! aik misaal bayan ki jati hai usay ghhor se suno. ke jin logon ko tum khuda ke siwa pkarte ho woh aik makhi bhi nahi bana satke agarchay is ke liye sab mujtma ho jaien. aur agar un se makhi koi cheez le jaye to usay is se churra nahi satke. taalib aur matloob ( yani abid aur mabood dono ) gay guzray hain
  22,74,un logon ne khuda ki qader jaisi karni chahiye thi nahi ki. kuch shak nahi ke khuda zabardast aur ghalib hai
  22,75,khuda firshton mein se pegham pohanchanay walay munhtakhib karleta hai aur insanon mein se bhi. be shak khuda suneney wala ( aur ) dekhnay wala hai
  22,76,jo un ke agay hai aur jin un ke peechay hai woh is se waaqif hai. aur sab kamon ka rujoo khuda hi ki taraf hai
  22,77,momino! ruku karte aur sjday karte aur apne perwar-digaar ki ibadat karte raho aur naik kaam karo taakay Falah pao
  22,78,aur khuda ( ki raah ) mein jehaad karo jaissa jehaad karne ka haq hai. is ne tum ko bargzidakiya hai aur tum par deen ki ( kisi baat ) mein tangi nahi ki. ( aur tumahray liye ) tumahray baap ibrahim ka deen ( pasandkiya ) usi ne pehlay ( yani pehli kitabon mein ) tumhara naam musalman rakha tha aur is kitaab mein bhi ( wohi naam rakha hai to jehaad karo ) taakay paighambar tumahray baray mein Shahid hon. aur tum logon ke muqablay mein Shahid aur namaz parho aur zakaat do aur khuda ke deen ki ( rassi ko ) pakdae raho. wohi tumhara dost hai. aur khoob dost aur khoob madadgaar hai
